                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                <placeName>Detroit</placeName>\n                <date>February 16th 1855</date>\n            </p>\n            <p>\n                <addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">\n                <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName>\n            </p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(3)\">Dear Sir!</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(4)\">I received yesterday<lb/> by American Express Company One case<lb/>\n                of books &amp; to day by mail your favor of the<lb/>\n                <date>10th</date> inst.</p>\n            <p>By examining the contents of the case we find<lb/> the following books</p>\n            <table cols=\"4\" rows=\"5\">\n                <row>\n                    <cell>6</cell>\n                    <cell>daily Prayer Books</cell>\n                    <cell/>\n                    <cell>20</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>3</cell>\n                    <cell>“ “ “</cell>\n                    <cell>Mor. Marb Edg</cell>\n                    <cell>$3.50</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>3</cell>\n                    <cell>“ “ “</cell>\n                    <cell>gold “</cell>\n                    <cell>4.25</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>3</cell>\n                    <cell>bibles</cell>\n                    <cell>Mor. Marb “</cell>\n                    <cell>9.00</cell>\n                </row>\n                <row>\n                    <cell>1</cell>\n                    <cell>set Pentateuch</cell>\n                    <cell>(5 volumes)</cell>\n                    <cell>16.50</cell>\n                </row>\n            </table>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Should you have intended to forward<lb/> any additional books this\n                case did not<lb/> contain them.</p>\n            <p>I shall endeavor when opportunities offer<lb/> to dispose of them &amp; also\n                    <sic>aquaint</sic>\n                <persName>Mr Adler</persName><lb/> of their arrival, in order to give him an<lb/>\n                opportunity to exert himself for the sale of<lb/> them.</p>\n            <p rend=\"indent(1)\">Any proceeds for the same recd. by me<lb/> will be forwarded to you\n                immediately.<lb/> The Express charges I advanced were $4—</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3xg9fx3j/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
